OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776687067
OL,3,CWhy the Robbins sacking is a crisis in
OL,4,Citself
OL,6,FThe prime minister "faces one of the
OL,7,Fworst crises in relations between
OL,8,Fministers and mandarins of modern
OL,9,Ftimes".
OL,11,FSo says Gus O'Donnell, the former
OL,12,Fcabinet secretary and ex-head of the
OL,13,Fcivil service.
OL,15,FSenior civil servants' confidence in
OL,16,FSir Keir Starmer and his government
OL,17,Fhas collapsed, says O'Donnell in the
OL,18,FTimes, because of his expedited
OL,19,Fsacking of the permanent under
OL,20,Fsecretary at the Foreign Office, Sir
OL,21,FOlly Robbins.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776687067
OL,3,CWhy the Robbins sacking is a crisis in
OL,4,Citself
OL,6,FHere is the nutshell of what this is
OL,7,Fabout and why this matters.
OL,9,FMPs and ministers have for years
OL,10,Fcomplained that civil servants are too
OL,11,Faverse to taking risks, that they
OL,12,Ffrustrate governments from executing
OL,13,Ftheir more radical plans, that - in
OL,14,Fthe most damning of caricatures -
OL,15,FWhitehall is a "blob".
OL,17,FRobbins, on the other hand, manifested
OL,18,Fthe opposite of blob-like blocking of
OL,19,Fministerial ambitions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776687067
OL,3,CWhy the Robbins sacking is a crisis in
OL,4,Citself
OL,6,FIn driving through UK Security
OL,7,FVetting's red light on the appointment
OL,8,Fof Peter Mandelson as US ambassador at
OL,9,Fthe end of January 2025, he was simply
OL,10,Fexecuting what the prime minister had
OL,11,Frevealed he wanted more than a month
OL,12,Fearlier - when on December 20, 2024
OL,13,FStarmer announced that, with the
OL,14,Fagreement of HM King Charles,
OL,15,FMandelson would be our person in
OL,16,FWashington.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776687067
OL,3,CWhy the Robbins sacking is a crisis in
OL,4,Citself
OL,6,FRobbins' reasonable judgment was that
OL,7,Fit was his responsibility to protect
OL,8,Fthe PM from the humiliation of having
OL,9,Fto cancel the appointment. Such a U-
OL,10,Fturn would have looked like a shambles
OL,11,Fbecause it would have been a shambles.
OL,13,FHere, however, is where it all gets
OL,14,Fmurkier.
OL,16,FRobbins made three more questionable
OL,17,Fjudgments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776687067
OL,3,CWhy the Robbins sacking is a crisis in
OL,4,Citself
OL,6,FFirst, that when Starmer made the
OL,7,Fappointment in December he could
OL,8,Freasonably have been expected to know
OL,9,Fwhy UK Security Vetting objected to
OL,10,Fhis appointment - because most of the
OL,11,Fnegatives about Mandelson (commercial
OL,12,Fconflicts of interest, business links
OL,13,Fto China and Russia, friendship with
OL,14,Fthe paedophile sex trafficker Jeffrey
OL,15,FEpstein) were both well known and in
OL,16,Fthe Cabinet Office's initial due
OL,17,Fdiligence paper.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776687067
OL,3,CWhy the Robbins sacking is a crisis in
OL,4,Citself
OL,6,FSo if there was nothing in the
OL,7,FDeveloped Vetting report that could
OL,8,Fhave shocked the PM, then many would
OL,9,Fsay Robbins was only doing what any PM
OL,10,Fwould want of a senior civil servant,
OL,11,Fnamely executing the revealed will of
OL,12,Fthe PM.
OL,14,FThat is what many officials are saying
OL,15,Fof Robbins - but we can't know the
OL,16,Ftruth of that because UKSV's evidence
OL,17,Ffor saying Mandelson was unfit for the
OL,18,Fjob has not, and may never be,
OL,19,Fpublished.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776687067
OL,3,CWhy the Robbins sacking is a crisis in
OL,4,Citself
OL,6,FSecond, Robbins had the power to
OL,7,Foverrule UKSV by putting in
OL,8,Fmitigations to manage the risks.
OL,10,FObviously, those risks weren't managed
OL,11,Fbecause Mandelson was sacked in
OL,12,FSeptember 2025 when emails leaked to
OL,13,FBloomberg revealed Mandelson remained
OL,14,Fsupportive of and friendly with
OL,15,FEpstein after he was imprisoned for
OL,16,Fsoliciting a child for sex.
OL,18,FBut again, the common sense of
OL,19,FRobbins' position can't be judged in
OL,20,Fthe absence of the UKSV report.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776687067
OL,3,CWhy the Robbins sacking is a crisis in
OL,4,Citself
OL,6,FThird, Robbins chose not to tell
OL,7,FStarmer or anyone close to Starmer
OL,8,Fthat UKSV had explicitly recommended
OL,9,Fthat Mandelson should not be appointed.
OL,11,FAnd he kept that somewhat resonant
OL,12,Ffact to himself even after Starmer
OL,13,Frepeatedly said in the Commons and in
OL,14,Fpress conferences that everything
OL,15,Fabout the vetting of Mandelson was
OL,16,Fship-shape and Bristol fashion, when
OL,17,Fobviously it wasn't.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776687067
OL,3,CWhy the Robbins sacking is a crisis in
OL,4,Citself
OL,6,FMost people can empathise with
OL,7,FStarmer's fury that Robbins - in
OL,8,FStarmer's view - has made him look a
OL,9,Fmonkey. But was that on its own just
OL,10,Fcause for Starmer and the foreign
OL,11,Fsecretary to sack Robbins
OL,12,Fperemptorily, as they did?
OL,14,FWe can all see how Starmer and Cooper
OL,15,Flost confidence in Robbins.
OL,17,FWe can all see that Robbins was daft
OL,18,Fin not covering his backside by
OL,19,Ftelling Starmer and his aides that he
OL,20,Fwas overruling UKSV.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776687067
OL,3,CWhy the Robbins sacking is a crisis in
OL,4,Citself
OL,6,FBut Robbins' primary, and most
OL,7,Fimportant, sin was to do what he
OL,8,Funderstandably believed was what the
OL,9,FPM wanted, without making a fuss about
OL,10,Fit.
OL,12,FWhich is what ministers in this
OL,13,Fgovernment repeatedly tell me they
OL,14,Fwant their officials to do, rather
OL,15,Fthan shilly-shallying and putting up
OL,16,Froadblocks all the time.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776687067
OL,3,CWhy the Robbins sacking is a crisis in
OL,4,Citself
OL,6,FAnd here is why O'Donnell is right
OL,7,Fthat the Robbins sacking is a genuine
OL,8,Fcrisis for government: Robbins was
OL,9,Fdismissed for taking a considered risk
OL,10,Fon behalf of his bosses; so, which
OL,11,Fpermanent secretary in his or her
OL,12,Fright mind will do that again?
OL,14,FStarmer can be seen in that sense to
OL,15,Fhave reinforced the blob tendency, to
OL,16,Fslow and frustrate government plans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776687067
OL,3,CWhy the Robbins sacking is a crisis in
OL,4,Citself
OL,6,FBut to repeat, the force of all I have
OL,7,Fargued hinges on whether we ever see
OL,8,Fthe reasons and evidence behind why
OL,9,FUKSV said Mandelson was too great a
OL,10,Frisk to be US ambassador. And whether
OL,11,Fthat can and will be revealed is
OL,12,Funclear.
OL,14,FThat means that the taint and stain
OL,15,Ffrom this episode will cling to both
OL,16,FStarmer and Robbins, which is contrary
OL,17,Fto natural justice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
